The set of .f90 programs here is a complete single sample

mc_singlef90 
single-sample metropolis calculation  for Laughlin nu = 1/m 

sq_m.f90
sampling code for producing s(q)

strip_m.f90
sampling code for strip occupations (for entanglement cuts)

energy_m.f90
sampling code for couomb energy


z_function_m.f90
routines for the modified sigma function

wf_tools.f90
tools for Laughlon wavefunction


new_coulomb_m.f90
implementation of ("lowest-landau-level") coulomb intercation


mc_tools_m.f90
Metropolis, etc

ziggurat.f90
random number generator


